name: Yu-Gi-Oh! Cardfus
description:
My first attempt at a dreambooth model worth sharing. Trained on 99 female Yu-Gi-Oh! cards ripped from Yu-Gi-Oh! Master Duel, though a male or two might have slipped in.

Doesn't require much special prompting, but "a cartoon girl/female/woman", "official art" and "yu-gi-oh!" seem to help.

meta.prompt: masterpiece, best quality, A female cartoon character, messy hair, spiky red hair, tomboy, [muscular], dark skin, weapon towards viewer, smirk, official art, yu-gi-oh!, solo
meta.negativePrompt: lowres, bad anatomy, bad hands, text, error, missing fingers, extra digit, fewer digits, cropped, worst quality, low quality, normal quality, jpeg artifacts,signature, watermark, username, blurry, artist name
